=head1 DESCRIPTION

Options for filtering the C<ListConfigurationPolicyAssociations>
response. You can filter by the Amazon Resource Name (ARN) or
universally unique identifier (UUID) of a configuration policy,
C<AssociationType>, or C<AssociationStatus>.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 AssociationStatus => Str

The current status of the association between a target and a
configuration policy.


=head2 AssociationType => Str

Indicates whether the association between a target and a configuration
was directly applied by the Security Hub delegated administrator or
inherited from a parent.


=head2 ConfigurationPolicyId => Str

The ARN or UUID of the configuration policy.



